SCOPE. This licence covers the CODE in this repository only. It does NOT cover:

1. The World Database on Protected Areas (WDPA) data. The WDPA and WD-OECM are the property of
   UNEP-WCMC and IUCN and their terms of use prohibit redistribution — the derived
   data file (includes/js/planet-data.js) is therefore NOT included in this
   repository. Regenerate it locally with scripts/fetch-wdpa.mjs and follow the
   citation and terms at https://www.protectedplanet.net/en/legal.

2. Earth imagery (includes/images/): NASA Blue Marble: Next Generation topography & bathymetry
   surface (earth_bathy_8k.jpg) and a NOAA ETOPO-derived relief map (earth_relief.jpg), both
   public domain. The earth-layers and
   maritime files (includes/js/planet-earth.js, planet-maritime.js) are built from Natural
   Earth (public domain) and Wikidata (CC0). The fungal-hotspots file (planet-fungi.js) is
   derived from the SPUN Underground Atlas (Van Nuland et al. 2025, Nature; Zenodo
   10.5281/zenodo.14871588), CC BY 4.0 — cite that work and acknowledge SPUN when reusing.

3. The LIAKO name, logo, branding and visual identity, which remain the property
   of Liako and may not be used to endorse or promote derived works.
